{"tid":651074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【推普壓粵】強調港人母語「絕對係廣東話」 陶傑狠批教局指鹿為馬 「母語」由母親第一身教佢識得講嘅語言","createTime":"2018-05-02T23:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T00:03:38.000Z","uid":35790,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ce28bea3a3b847ccf0bff49fcf3488ee931816d3","tid":651074,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T23:24:18.000Z","msg":"【推普壓粵】強調港人母語「絕對係廣東話」 陶傑狠批教局指鹿為馬<br />\n<br />\n教育局近日被揭於2013年向全港小學派發的普通話課程配套資料中，使用由中大研究普通話學者撰寫的文章，指「香港漢族人的母語是漢語」，粵語只屬方言及「地域變體」而非「母語」，普通話才是「正規的語言教育」。專欄作家陶傑批評說法「大錯特錯」，強調香港人的母語「絕對係廣東話」，慨歎現時已「進入指鹿為馬嘅時代」。<br />\n<br />\n陶傑稱，<span style=\"color: red;\">根據牛津劍橋英語字典，「母語」（mother tongue）一詞的意思是小孩出生後，「由母親第一身教佢識得講嘅語言」</span>，香港政府由前特首董建華年代開始推行母語教學，亦一直以廣東話進行。<br />\n對於有報道指文憑試通識科研棄1至5**只設「及格」與「不及格」，陶傑稱自己3年前已說過通識不能評級，「只有合格不合格」，但他批評香港的通識教育「方向方法全部錯」，不應只改評核標準，應「早取消早着」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180502/58145131\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180502%2F58145131&d=oFU%2BnXDTYpKhD99QBI6jNAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=748223fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180502%2F58145131&h=75b4fab5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180502/58145131</a>"},{"pid":"dc8137b8d6ba4382f812f81aa433d12add615169","tid":651074,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T23:29:52.000Z","msg":"支那人所生唔係香港人"},{"pid":"bbea2572260579e7772bd438c06594835951fb28","tid":651074,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T23:44:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9085447518bf205831da3f9999c0b7c1edde3f90","tid":651074,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T23:53:13.000Z","msg":"世界上只有一種母語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab8babeb0cd03f51a04e5d4e4f4849c7452ead7","tid":651074,"uid":169662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T23:57:56.000Z","msg":"條「研究普通話學者」係乜水，官方語言同母語都唔識分"},{"pid":"b2a13a998bcefeda5d083423261ac106df724033","tid":651074,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T00:02:41.000Z","msg":"普通話係滿洲人入關後學講北京話"},{"pid":"ee6b8465f6f70552e3782c830fca5fc67a9b7be7","tid":651074,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T00:03:38.000Z","msg":"陶傑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}